d to bringing cutting-edge technology into your everyday life. We believe in creating intuitive, reliable, and secure solutions that simplify your home management and enhance your well-being. Our commitment is to innovation and user-centric design, ensuring your home is always a sanctuary.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"features\" id=\"contact\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3 style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">Get In Touch</h3>\n            <p style=\"margin-bottom: 40px;\">Ready to transform your home? Contact us today for a consultation.</p>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                 <div class=\"feature-item\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-phone\"></i>\n                    <h4>Call Us</h4>\n                    <p>+1 (800) 123-4567</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-envelope\"></i>\n                    <h4>Email Us</h4>\n                    <p>info@aurasmarthome.com</p>\n                </div>\n                 <div class=\"feature-item\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-map-marker-alt\"></i>\n                    <h4>Visit Us</h4>\n                    <p>123 Aura Way, Smart City, SC 98765</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2024 Aura Smart Home. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Smooth scrolling for navigation links\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}